trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilder" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilder" /> .

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilderCollection> class does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilderCollection> classe não se refere a qualquer elemento real no arquivo de configuração subjacentes.

trans-unit.source: It is a construct that allows easy access to the compilation information it contains.
